Package: jmoviLLMAssistant
Type: Package
Title: Jamovi LLM Assistant – Statistical Analysis with AI Guidance
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-27
Authors@R: person("CFM Project Chiklod",
                   "Department of Community and Family Medicine, AIIMS Bhopal",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "cfm@aiimsbhopal.edu.in")
Maintainer: CFM Project Chiklod <cfm@aiimsbhopal.edu.in>
Description: A Jamovi module integrating Google Gemini LLM for AI-guided
    statistical analysis. Provides a structured three-phase workflow:
    (1) input validation and data quality checks,
    (2) comprehensive statistical assumption testing (normality, homogeneity,
    independence, linearity, multicollinearity), and
    (3) hypothesis testing with effect sizes, confidence intervals, and
    plain-language AI-generated interpretations.
